      <title>韩国对美元债券收益率跌至历史最低水平，对韩元造成打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/korean-bond-yield-plumbs-record-lows-against-us-in-blow-to-won</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国债券收益率相对于美国国债收益率连续跌至历史最低水平，这给已经受到政治危机重创的韩元带来了进一步压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/korean-bond-yield-plumbs-record-lows-against-us-in-blow-to-won</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 00:09:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
